Introduction

Byulzzi was a three-member trot girl group under THE NEW Entertainment. They debuted on August 23, 2020, with their single album, Bbibbo Bbibbo but due to inactivity since 2020 and Jihye joining 3piece (ONAIR at the time) as a pre-debut member, it is assumed they disbanded.
